SUMMARY:Women's Bible Study
DESCRIPTION:Join the women of our parish for a transformative journey of Bible study\, prayer and fellowship in the parish house library. This gathering is an opportunity to deepen your relationships\, share your experiences\, and grow in faith together. Let’s lift each other up and spark inspiration in our hearts as we explore the Word of God. Women’s Bible study meets on the 3rd Sunday of every month. Come\, and be a part of this uplifting community! \nIf you have any questions\, please click here to email Kristy Clark.
URL:https://www.saintjameslancaster.org/event/womens-bible-study/2026-03-15/
LOCATION:Saint James Parish House\, 119 North Duke Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
