SUMMARY:Youth Group
DESCRIPTION:New Topics Every Month\nOpen to all 6th–12th graders\, Youth Group meets every third Sunday of the month from 5:00 – 6:30 PM. Dinner is provided\, so bring your appetite\, bring a friend\, and get ready for a fun evening. We’ll provide dinner and good vibes\, just come hungry and curious. \nFor more information\, click here to email StephJo Wise\, Director of Children\, Youth and Families.
